summary: Header file for class AITransferPort, inherits from NSObject and conforms to NSCoding protocol. Contains two properties: scene (AIKVPointer type) and canset (AIKVPointer type). Offers a singleton-like method newWithScene:canset: to create instances of AITransferPort with specified parameters.
